{"data":[{"date":"13:32 10/07","title":"Kh\u00f4ng khi\u0301 World Cup 2018 tr\u00e2\u0300m l\u0103\u0323ng \u01a1\u0309 la\u0300ng qu\u00ea cu\u0309a \u0111\u00f4\u0323i bo\u0301ng m\u1eafc k\u1eb9t trong hang","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/10/khong-khi-world-cup-2018-tram-lang-o-lang-que-cua-doi-bong-mac-ket-trong-hang.jpg","new_desc":"${8_news_content2}","new_url":"","id":"4108","checkdouble":"190850"},{"date":"14:48 10/07","title":"C\u1ef1u sao Arsenal b\u1ecb b\u1eaft gi\u1eef v\u00ec t\u00ecnh nghi c\u1ed1 \u00fd g\u00e2y h\u1ecfa ho\u1ea1n","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/10/cuu-sao-arsenal-bi-bat-giu-vi-tinh-nghi-co-y-gay-hoa-hoan.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1ea3nh s\u00e1t nghi ng\u1edd Emmanuel Eboue g\u00e2y ra \u0111\u00e1m ch\u00e1y b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 \u1edf Enfield, London.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">Theo Mirror, Emmanuel Eboue b\u1ecb b\u1eaft v\u00e0o l\u00fac 17h chi\u1ec1u 7/7, theo gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ecba ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. C\u1ef1u h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Arsenal b\u1ecb \u0111\u01b0a t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed3n c\u1ea3nh s\u00e1t \u1edf ph\u00eda B\u1eafc London v\u00ec t\u00ecnh nghi g\u00e2y ra v\u1ee5 ch\u00e1y b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 \u1edf Enfield h\u00f4m 30/6.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u1ea1n b\u00e8 kh\u00f4ng kh\u1ecfi lo l\u1eafng cho Eboue v\u00ec anh \u0111ang \u1edf trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n b\u1ea5t \u1ed5n v\u1ec1 t\u00e2m l\u00fd. H\u1ecd s\u1ee3 r\u1eb1ng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1edd Bi\u1ec3n Nga kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1n thu\u00ea lu\u1eadt s\u01b0 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 cho m\u00ecnh sau khi b\u1ecb v\u1ee3 c\u0169 l\u1eeba, chi\u1ebfm \u0111\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"C\u1ef1u sao Arsenal b\u1ecb b\u1eaft gi\u1eef v\u00ec t\u00ecnh nghi c\u1ed1 \u00fd g\u00e2y h\u1ecfa ho\u1ea1n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"C\u1ef1u sao Arsenal b\u1ecb b\u1eaft gi\u1eef v\u00ec t\u00ecnh nghi c\u1ed1 \u00fd g\u00e2y h\u1ecfa ho\u1ea1n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/eboue1-4581-1531131441.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Eboue hi\u1ec7n tay tr\u1eafng khi ly h\u00f4n c\u00f4 v\u1ee3 Aurelie Bertrand. \u1ea2nh: Mirror.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\no\u1ea1t s\u1ea1ch t\u00e0i s\u1ea3n. Tuy nhi\u00ean, ch\u1ec9 m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y sau khi b\u1ecb b\u1eaft, Eboue \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ea3 t\u1ef1 do. C\u1ea3nh s\u00e1t cho bi\u1ebft h\u1ecd s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec1u tra th\u00eam g\u00ec v\u1ec1 v\u1ee5 vi\u1ec7c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nEboue t\u1eebng c\u00f3 214 tr\u1eadn kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Arsenal trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n 2004-2011. Anh hi\u1ec7n l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ef1 do sau khi chia tay CLB Sunderland v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2016. Th\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Eboue \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1eddi thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho \u0111\u1ed9i Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Arsenal trong tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Bernabeu.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, Eboue cho bi\u1ebft: \"B\u00e2y gi\u1edd, \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u00f4i mong mu\u1ed1n nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa. T\u00f4i v\u1eabn c\u00f2n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ai b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh c\u1ea3. T\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y nh\u01b0 b\u1ecb b\u1ecf r\u01a1i. T\u00f4i t\u1eebng c\u00f3 v\u1ee3 con nh\u01b0ng gi\u1edd t\u00f4i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f4 \u0111\u1ed9c\".<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau khi ly h\u00f4n c\u00f4 v\u1ee3 Aurelie Bertrand, Eboue t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t tri\u1ec7u ph\u00fa tr\u1edf n\u00ean tr\u1eafng tay. To\u00e0n b\u1ed9 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n v\u00e0 b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n anh c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c sang t\u00ean cho Aurelie. \"V\u1ee3 t\u00f4i \u0111\u01b0a b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 gi\u1ea5y t\u1edd n\u00e0o t\u00f4i c\u0169ng k\u00fd b\u1edfi c\u00f4 \u1ea5y l\u00e0 v\u1ee3 t\u00f4i\", Eboue k\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i. </div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4107","checkdouble":"190853"},{"date":"12:55 10/07","title":"T\u00e2n binh Juventus h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng c\u00f9ng Ronaldo","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/6/emre-can-hao-huc-truoc-co-hoi-choi-bong-cung-ronaldo.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Emre Can t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng c\u00f9ng Ronaldo t\u1ea1i Juventus \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m sau.</h2><h2>Can h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i c\u00f9ng Ronaldo</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y cho th\u1ea5y Juventus \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u euro t\u1edbi Real Madrid \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a Ronaldo. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/nguoi-juventus-som-mo-ve-song-sat-tai-hop-ronaldo-higuain-184-190405.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus</span> d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn s\u1ebd s\u1edbm di\u1ec5n ra.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Emre Can h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Emre Can h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/Emre-Can-hao-huc-truoc-vien-canh-Ronaldo-gia-nhap-Juventus-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Emre Can h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd l\u00e0m t\u0103ng \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Juventus c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 Serie A. Sau khi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Juve theo d\u1ea1ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 do, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Emre Can th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn anh c\u0169ng vui m\u1eebng n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f9ng CR7 t\u1ea1i Juventus Arena.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cT\u00f4i ngh\u0129 b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f9ng Ronaldo. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft Juventus c\u00f3 li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi anh \u1ea5y hay kh\u00f4ng. T\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 t\u1eadp trung ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n m\u00ecnh. Nh\u01b0ng s\u1ebd th\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t n\u1ebfu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng c\u00f9ng Ronaldo t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y\u201d.</em></div>\r\n<h2>Can quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u00fap Juve chinh ph\u1ee5c C1</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Emre Can \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e0nh 4 n\u0103m thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Liverpool nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c danh hi\u1ec7u n\u00e0o. D\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f9ng The Kop l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o 3 tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft League Cup, Europa League v\u00e0 Champions League nh\u01b0ng vinh quang v\u1eabn l\u1ea9n tr\u00e1nh Liverpool v\u00e0 Emre Can.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong khi \u0111\u00f3, Juventus \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh t\u1edbi 7 danh hi\u1ec7u Scudetto li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp. Tuy v\u1eady, \u201cL\u00e3o b\u00e0\u201d \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua 22 n\u0103m li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u0103ng quang Champions League. V\u00e0 Emre Can hy v\u1ecdng anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Bianconeri v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch C1 trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cT\u00f4i ngh\u0129 \u01b0u ti\u00ean quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Serie A r\u1ed3i sau \u0111\u00f3 m\u1edbi l\u00e0 Champions League. Juventus ch\u01b0a v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch C1 trong 22 n\u0103m qua v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng nh\u01b0ng \u01b0u ti\u00ean quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t v\u1eabn l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng Serie A\u201d.<br>\r\n</em><br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Ronaldo:<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/buffon-noi-gi-truoc-vien-canh-juve-chieu-mo-ronaldo-421-190836.html\">Buffon n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh Juve chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Ronaldo?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-ngay-107-48-gio-nua-ronaldo-se-la-nguoi-cua-juve-184-190814.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 10/7: 48 gi\u1edd n\u1eefa, Ronaldo s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Juve</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</strong><br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4106","checkdouble":"190838"},{"date":"16:02 10/07","title":"Ronaldo s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Juventus?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/10/ronaldo-se-da-o-dau-trong-doi-hinh-juventus.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Cristiano Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 th\u1eddi gian, d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin ph\u00e1t huy h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u euro.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">4-3-1-2 v\u1edbi Ronaldo v\u00e0 Higuain \u0111\u00e1 cao nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/lo-so-ao-cua-ronaldo-o-juventus-180-190540.html\" target=\"_blank\">Cristiano Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus</span>, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Gonzalo Higuain kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u00e2n s\u00fat 31 tu\u1ed5i r\u1ea5t vui v\u1edbi th\u00f4ng tin n\u00e0y. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i Juventus \u0111\u1ec3 s\u00e1t c\u00e1nh b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh CR7.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cristiano Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus Allegri c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 n\u00e0o h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Cristiano Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus Allegri c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 n\u00e0o h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/Cristiano-Ronaldo-toi-Juventus-Allegri-co-the-van-hanh-so-do-nao-hinh-anh.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>4-3-1-2 v\u1edbi Ronaldo v\u00e0 Higuain \u0111\u00e1 cao nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Th\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi n\u1ebfu Ronaldo h\u1ee3p t\u00e1c v\u1edbi Higuain. H\u1ecd bi\u1ebft nhau r\u1ea5t r\u00f5, h\u1ecd ch\u01a1i kho\u1ea3ng 80 tr\u1eadn v\u1edbi nhau. Ronaldo v\u00e0 Higuain l\u00e0 2 trong s\u1ed1 nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, s\u1ef1 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p gi\u1eefa h\u1ecd r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i&rdquo;.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Ronaldo, HLV Massimiliano Allegri ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng 4-3-1-2 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. \u1ede tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa, Matuidi, Pjanic v\u00e0 Can l\u00e0 b\u1ed9 ba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tin t\u01b0\u1edfng. Dybala ch\u01a1i \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u1ed9 c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 cung c\u1ea5p b\u00f3ng cho Ronaldo v\u00e0 Higuain.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nDybala l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o v\u00f4 h\u1ea1n, nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ch\u1ecdc khe c\u1ee7a anh mang \u0111\u1ebfn r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho c\u00e1c ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o. V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 c\u1ee7a Dybala, Ronaldo v\u00e0 Higuain s\u1ebd c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1993 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u00fat xa c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t, vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n hai ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u0169ng gi\u00fap anh ph\u00e1t huy h\u1ebft kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>4-3-3 v\u1edbi b\u1ed9 ba t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng Ronaldo, Higuain v\u00e0 Dybala</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 4-3-3 th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Allegri v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh. Theo \u0111\u00f3, Higuain, Dybala v\u00e0 Mandzukic l\u00e0 b\u1ed9 ba th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng. Khi Mandzukic kh\u00f4ng ra s\u00e2n th\u00ec Douglas Costa \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn thay th\u1ebf.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"4-3-3 voi bo ba tan cong Ronaldo, Higuain va Dybala\" title=\"4-3-3 v\u1edbi b\u1ed9 ba t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng Ronaldo, Higuain v\u00e0 Dybala\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/2.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>4-3-3 v\u1edbi b\u1ed9 ba t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng Ronaldo, Higuain v\u00e0 Dybala</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nS\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 v\u1edbi 3 m\u0169i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng gi\u00fap Juventus mang v\u1ec1 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. \u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Ronaldo, s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 4-3-3 h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd c\u00f2n ph\u00e1t huy nhi\u1ec1u hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 h\u01a1n n\u1eefa.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng g\u1ed3m 3 m\u0169i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, Ronaldo, Higuain v\u00e0 Dybala s\u00e1t c\u00e1nh b\u00ean nhau. CR7 ch\u01a1i b\u00ean c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i, Dybala ch\u01a1i c\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n c\u00f2n Higuain ch\u01a1i \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed m\u0169i nh\u1ecdn. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u1edf ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, b\u1edfi v\u1eady s\u1ee9c t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng t\u1eeb h\u1ecd s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t kh\u1ee7ng&nbsp;khi\u1ebfp.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa, Juventus c\u00f3 chuy\u00ean gia l\u00e0m b\u00f3ng nh\u01b0 Pjanic, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i gi\u1eefa h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Bosnia duy tr\u00ec s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn trong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, b\u1edfi v\u1eady anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m nhi\u1ec7m vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ea5p b\u00f3ng cho b\u1ed9 ba t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi Emre Can v\u00e0 Blaise Matuidi \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n, Juventus c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n qu\u00e1 lo l\u1eafng khi \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng. H\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f9ng s\u1ef1 tr\u1ee3 gi\u00fap c\u1ee7a 2 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng trong t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>4-2-3-1 v\u1edbi Ronaldo \u0111\u00e1 cao nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Ronaldo, m\u1ecdi s\u1ef1 ch\u00fa \u00fd s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed5 d\u1ed3n v\u00e0o CR7. Khi \u0111\u00f3 t\u1ea7m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Higuain v\u00e0o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Juventus s\u1ebd gi\u1ea3m \u0111i \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3, khi \u0111\u00f3 anh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed9i \u0110KV\u0110 Serie A \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"4-2-3-1 voi Ronaldo da cao nhat tren hang cong\" title=\"4-2-3-1 v\u1edbi Ronaldo \u0111\u00e1 cao nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/3.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>4-2-3-1 v\u1edbi Ronaldo \u0111\u00e1 cao nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Higuain r\u1eddi Juventus, HLV Allegri kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i lo l\u1eafng b\u1edfi Ronaldo ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed do c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 31 tu\u1ed5i \u1edf l\u1ea1i. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 4-2-3-1 v\u1edbi CR7 \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed cao nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi s\u1ef1 tr\u1ee3 gi\u00fap c\u1ee7a Dybala t\u1eeb ph\u00eda sau, Ronaldo s\u1ebd c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m. M\u00f9a v\u1eeba qua, ng\u00f4i sao 25 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra t\u1edbi 18 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho Higuain nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 2 trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u1ec3n h\u00f3a th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi Ronaldo thay v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a Higuain, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ed1 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a Dybala \u1edf m\u00f9a t\u1edbi s\u1ebd t\u0103ng l\u00ean \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3. V\u1edbi Douglas Costa v\u00e0 Mario Mandzukic b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh Dybala, Juventus s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng v\u0169 kh\u00ed \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>4-3-3 v\u1edbi Dybala, Ronaldo v\u00e0 Douglas Costa tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Higuain r\u1eddi Juventus ho\u1eb7c HLV Allegri kh\u00f4ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina, \u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 4-3-3 v\u1edbi Paulo Dybala, Cristiano Ronaldo v\u00e0 Douglas Costa l\u00e0 3 m\u0169i nh\u1ecdn tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"4-3-3 voi Dybala, Ronaldo va Douglas Costa tren hang cong\" title=\"4-3-3 v\u1edbi Dybala, Ronaldo v\u00e0 Douglas Costa tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/4.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>4-3-3 v\u1edbi Dybala, Ronaldo v\u00e0 Douglas Costa tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y, Ronaldo s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung phong, Dybala v\u00e0 Douglas Costa ch\u01a1i \u1edf hai c\u00e1nh. N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 CR7 s\u1edf h\u1eefu kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u1ea1y ch\u1ed7 t\u1ed1t th\u00ec t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Dybala v\u00e0 Douglas Costa, s\u1ef1 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p gi\u1eefa b\u1ed9 ba n\u00e0y s\u1ebd \u0111em l\u1ea1i s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMiralem Pjanic s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i cao nh\u1ea5t n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea5p b\u00f3ng cho b\u1ed9 ba t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Bosnia c\u0169ng c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o, nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ch\u1ecdc khe s\u1eafc l\u1eb9m c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u00f9ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u1ea1y ch\u1ed7 thi\u00ean t\u00e0i c\u1ee7a Ronaldo h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Juventus&nbsp;mang v\u1ec1 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4105","checkdouble":"190857"},{"date":"15:52 10/07","title":"Chelsea t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Real cho Hazard","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/31/chelsea-tu-choi-loi-de-nghi-dau-tien-cua-real-cho-hazard.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Real Madrid mua Eden Hazard nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 53 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd v\u1eeba b\u1ecb Chelsea t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n Hazard cho Real v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 53 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nReal Madrid nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd m\u1ea5t Ronaldo v\u00e0o tay Juventus, CR7 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb ra m\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin. S\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn \u1edf s\u00e2n Bernabeu.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chi 53 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng Real Madrid mua Eden Hazard kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chi 53 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng Real Madrid mua Eden Hazard kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/31/Chi-53-trieu-bang-Real-Madrid-mua-Eden-Hazard-khong-thanh-cong-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Eden Hazard cho Real v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 53 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Lopetegui mu\u1ed1n d\u00f9ng s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n b\u00e1n Ronaldo \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 thay th\u1ebf, c\u1ea3 nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Perez \u0111\u1ec1u nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Eden Hazard c\u1ee7a Chelsea. Trong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Los Blancos.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHazard \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, anh c\u0169ng duy tr\u00ec s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, Express kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-chi-co-the-chieu-mo-hazard-voi-mot-dieu-kien-180-184658.html\" target=\"_blank\">Real Madrid mua Eden Hazard </span>nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 53 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd v\u1eeba b\u1ecb Chelsea t\u1eeb\u00a0ch\u1ed1i. The Blues kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n Los Blancos \u0111\u01b0a ra ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c h\u1ecd nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Real c\u1ea7n t\u0103ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua Hazard</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Con s\u1ed1 60 tri\u1ec7u euro m\u00e0 Real Madrid \u0111\u01b0a ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Chelsea b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao 27 tu\u1ed5i. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London \u01b0u ti\u00ean gi\u1eef c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 \u1edf l\u1ea1i, trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i b\u00e1n anh h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n thu v\u1ec1 100 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Eden Hazard Chelsea\" title=\"Eden Hazard Chelsea\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/31/chelsea-tu-choi-loi-de-nghi-dau-tien-cua-real-cho-hazard.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea mu\u1ed1n 100 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho Eden Hazard\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0 th\u1ebf c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n m\u00e0 Chelsea mu\u1ed1n thu v\u1ec1 g\u1ea5p \u0111\u00f4i l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean m\u00e0 Real \u0111\u01b0a ra. H\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Hazard v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge v\u1eabn c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2020, b\u1edfi v\u1eady Chelsea c\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n h\u00e9t gi\u00e1 cao cho ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nB\u1ea3n th\u00e2n Hazard v\u1eabn gi\u1eef im l\u1eb7ng v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, nh\u01b0ng ngay c\u1ea3 khi anh t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Chelsea th\u00ec Real v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i chi ra m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn h\u01a1n con s\u1ed1 53 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nN\u1ebfu Hazard \u0111\u1ebfn g\u1eb7p BL\u0110 Chelsea \u0111\u00f2i ra \u0111i, khi \u0111\u00f3 The Blues s\u1ebd gi\u1ea3m gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, nh\u01b0ng s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n m\u00e0 Real b\u1ecf ra s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng d\u01b0\u1edbi 80 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. V\u1edbi TTCN \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 b\u1ecb th\u1ed5i gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao v\u00e0 80 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho Hazard c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n h\u1ee3p l\u00fd.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4104","checkdouble":"190852"},{"date":"17:40 10/07","title":"Eden Hazard t\u1edbi La Liga nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i Real?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/7/eden-hazard-toi-la-liga-nhung-khong-phai-real.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Barca mu\u1ed1n mua Eden Hazard, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 100 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t Real Madrid trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Barca gia nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh Hazard</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Eden Hazard l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ec1 t\u00e0i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e1o ch\u00ed khai th\u00e1c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn. Real quan t\u00e2m Hazard, ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Perez mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Barca mu\u1ed1n mua Eden Hazard v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u euro \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Barca mu\u1ed1n mua Eden Hazard v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u euro \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/Barca-muon-mua-Eden-Hazard-voi-gia-100-trieu-euro-o-He-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Barca mu\u1ed1n mua Eden Hazard</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Real mua Hazard b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tr\u1edf n\u00ean kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n khi h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. Theo Sport c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha, Barca mu\u1ed1n mua Eden Hazard, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi \u0111\u1eadm mua ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBarca v\u1eeba nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Antoine Griezmann t\u1eeb Atletico Madrid, h\u1ecd nh\u1eafm Hazard thay c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p. \u0110\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t Real Madrid trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ea9y nhanh t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBarca s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n m\u00e0 Chelsea y\u00eau c\u1ea7u, theo \u0111\u00f3 h\u1ecd s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi t\u1edbi 100 tri\u1ec7u euro cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 The Sun kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chelsea-tu-choi-loi-de-nghi-dau-tien-cua-real-cho-hazard-172-190852.html\" target=\"_blank\">Chelsea t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n Hazard cho Real</span> v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 60 tri\u1ec7u euro.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Barca c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Hazard</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng gi\u1eefa Hazard v\u1edbi Chelsea ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2020, The Blues \u0111\u00e3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n mu\u1ed1n gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 nh\u01b0ng anh \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh mu\u1ed1n ki\u1ec3m ch\u1ee9ng tham v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Chelsea tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00f3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi hay kh\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Eden Hazard Chelsea\" title=\"Eden Hazard Chelsea\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/31/hazard-nen-tu-choi-real-de-tro-thanh-huyen-thoai-cua-chelsea.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u00e1n Eden Hazard \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Roman Abramovich \u0111ang t\u1ee9c gi\u1eadn v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i \u201cc\u00e2u gi\u1edd\u201d t\u1eeb ph\u00eda Hazard, Mirror kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u00f4ng n\u00e0y s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ee3p l\u00fd.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nReal \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n quan t\u00e2m Hazard t\u1eeb kh\u00e1 l\u00e2u, nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i quy\u1ebft li\u1ec7t trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. N\u1ebfu Barca \u0111\u1ea9y nhanh ti\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n, \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n m\u00e0 Chelsea y\u00eau c\u1ea7u v\u00e0 tr\u1ea3 l\u01b0\u01a1ng r\u1ea5t cao cho Hazard, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHazard hi\u1ec7n v\u1eabn \u0111ang c\u00f9ng \u0110T B\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf World Cup 2018, ng\u00f4i sao 27 tu\u1ed5i m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1ecdi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e1 cho Real.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1991 \u01b0u ti\u00ean t\u1edbi Bernabeu n\u1ebfu r\u1eddiChelsea, nh\u01b0ng trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Los Blancos kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i th\u00e1i quy\u1ebft li\u1ec7t th\u00ec anh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn chuy\u1ec7n t\u1edbi Barca.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4103","checkdouble":"190865"},{"date":"11:28 10/07","title":"HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110N\u00c1?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/4/20/hlv-hoang-anh-tuan-noi-gi-sau-that-bai-cua-u19-viet-nam-tai-giai-u19-dna.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a \u0111\u00e1ng th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng tr\u01b0\u1edbc U19 Singapore, HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n t\u1ecf ra kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 bu\u1ed3n m\u00e0 \u00f4ng cho r\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u khu v\u1ef1c s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t cho c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2.</h2><h2>HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/HLV-Hoang-Anh-Tuan-noi-gi-sau-that-bai-cua-U19-Viet-Nam-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n kh\u00f4ng bu\u1ed3n sau khi U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn thua 0-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Indonesia, c\u00e1nh c\u1eeda v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf n\u00ean r\u1ea5t h\u1eb9p v\u1edbi U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00fang nh\u01b0 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i s\u1edbm d\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc b\u1edfi \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u1ee7a v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, U19 Th\u00e1i Lan \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Indonesia v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-1, trong khi U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ec3 Singapore c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a 2-2.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a kh\u00f4ng t\u1ecf ra qu\u00e1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y. Thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y s\u1ebd t\u1ed1t cho c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o VCK U19 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;H\u00f4m nay c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi tinh th\u1ea7n kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n k\u00e9m tr\u00ean s\u00e2n. \u0110\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 n\u0103m th\u1ee9 hai li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i d\u1eebng ch\u00e2n t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng d\u00f9 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, t\u00f4i cho r\u1eb1ng th\u1ea5y b\u1ea1i c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t cho ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. Qua gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ebd c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho VCK U19 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 t\u1ea1i Indonesia v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 10 t\u1edbi&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u00f4ng c\u1ea3m cho HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n khi \u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng mang theo l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t \u1edf gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y khi nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang ph\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho c\u00e1c CLB \u1edf c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0 h\u1ea1ng nh\u00ec. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch, k\u1ebft th\u00fac gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1, \u0110T U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd c\u00f3 hai chuy\u1ebfn t\u1eadp hu\u1ea5n d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n t\u1ea1i Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u00e0 Qatar tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Indonesia \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh chinh ph\u1ee5c t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 d\u1ef1 U20 World Cup 2019.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-u19-viet-nam-22-u19-singapore-u19-dong-nam-a-2018-325-190804.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/7/tong-hop-u19-viet-nam-22-u19-singapore-u19-dong-nam-a-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-u19-viet-nam-22-u19-singapore-u19-dong-nam-a-2018-325-190804.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam 2-2 U19 Singapore (U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018)</span><br>\r\nD\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0 to\u00e0n thua c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 song th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 n\u1ed5i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1m bi\u1ec7t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1ed9t...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/u19-viet-nam-vs-u19-singapore-ngay-hom-nay-97-372-190790.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/7/u19-viet-nam-vs-u19-singapore-ngay-hom-nay-97.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/u19-viet-nam-vs-u19-singapore-ngay-hom-nay-97-372-190790.html\">U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam 2-2 U19 Singapore (KT): Chia tay gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018 trong n\u1ed7i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng</span><br>\r\nD\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0 to\u00e0n thua c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 song th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 n\u1ed5i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1m bi\u1ec7t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1ed9t...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4102","checkdouble":"190845"},{"date":"09:05 10/07","title":"M.U \u0111i th\u00eam m\u1ed9t b\u01b0\u1edbc n\u1eefa \u1edf th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Milinkovic-Savic","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/16/mu-di-them-mot-buoc-nua-o-thuong-vu-chieu-mo-milinkovicsavic.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>CLB Man United m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i m\u1edbi m\u1edf ra hi v\u1ecdng v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c s\u1ebd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Sergej Milinkovic-Savic \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Italia cho Lazio.</h2><h2>M.U c\u1eed \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n sang \u00dd \u0111\u1ec3 th\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ea3o v\u1ee5&nbsp;Milinkovic-Savic&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Milinkovic-Savic\" title=\"Milinkovic-Savic\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/9/Lazio-muon-mua-Aaron-Ramsey-thay-Milinkovic-Savic-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>M.U \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eed \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n sang \u00dd \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp th\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ea3o v\u1ec1 phi v\u1ee5 Milinkovic-Savic</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, CLB Man United \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eed ng\u01b0\u1eddi sang Italia \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp g\u1eb7p g\u1ee1 v\u00e0 trao \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c quan ch\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a Lazio \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1edbm ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Serbia, Sergej Milinkovic-Savic. Th\u00f4ng tin n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edd nh\u1eadt b\u00e1o ti\u1ebfng \u00dd Il Messaggero&nbsp;ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i c\u1ee7a M.U cho th\u1ea5y h\u1ecd \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh anh c\u0169ng \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn t\u1eeb Real Madrid. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eed ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Lazio v\u1edbi mong mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Milinkovic-Savic v\u1ec1 Bernabeu. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sergej Milinkovic-Savic n\u0103m nay ch\u1ec9 m\u1edbi 23 tu\u1ed5i nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y tri\u1ec3n v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u. Savic s\u1edf h\u1eefu th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh l\u00ed t\u01b0\u1edfng (1m91), c\u00f3 k\u0129 thu\u1eadt, t\u1ea7m nh\u00ecn, s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh l\u1eabn kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u0103n b\u00e0n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. \u0110\u00f3 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 l\u00fd do gi\u00fap anh thu h\u00fat s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a hai \u00f4ng l\u1edbn b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi l\u00e0 M.U v\u00e0 Real.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y, hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng tr\u00ean s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Seria A nh\u1ea3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 v\u1eeba ph\u1ea3i. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Lazio, Claudio Lotito \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb kh\u1eaft khe khi ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ec3 Savic ra \u0111i khi nh\u1eadn v\u1ec1 155 tri\u1ec7u euro.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4101","checkdouble":"190819"},{"date":"11:16 10/07","title":"T\u00e2n binh Bernd Leno ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ch\u1ecdn s\u1ed1 \u00e1o \u1edf Arsenal","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/10/tan-binh-bernd-leno-chinh-thuc-chon-so-ao-o-arsenal.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Bernd Leno m\u1eb7c \u00e1o s\u1ed1 19 \u1edf Arsenal, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ed1 \u00e1o trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi. Anh r\u1ea5t th\u00edch s\u1ed1 1 nh\u01b0ng s\u1ed1 \u00e1o n\u00e0y \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 Petr Cech.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Bernd Leno ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ch\u1ecdn s\u1ed1 \u00e1o \u1edf Arsenal</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Bayer Leverkusen, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Bernd Leno m\u1eb7c \u00e1o s\u1ed1 1. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 22 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, anh c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t th\u00edch kho\u00e1c l\u00ean m\u00ecnh chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o s\u1ed1 1 \u1edf s\u00e2n Emirates.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bernd Leno m\u1eb7c \u00e1o s\u1ed1 19 \u1edf Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Bernd Leno m\u1eb7c \u00e1o s\u1ed1 19 \u1edf Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/tan-binh-bernd-leno-chinh-thuc-chon-so-ao-o-arsenal.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Bernd Leno m\u1eb7c \u00e1o s\u1ed1 19 \u1edf Arsenal</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, Arsenal x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn \u00e1o s\u1ed1 1 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 Petr Cech, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi C\u1ed9ng H\u00f2a S\u00e9c \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u1ecf \u00e1o s\u1ed1 33 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111eo \u00e1o s\u1ed1 1 t\u1eeb m\u00f9a 2018/19.\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ed1 \u00e1o nh\u01b0 mong mu\u1ed1n Bernd Leno m\u1eb7c \u00e1o s\u1ed1 19 \u1edf Arsenal, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 \u00e1o c\u00f3 \u00fd ngh\u0129a \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 tu\u1ed5i khi anh ra m\u1eaft Bayer Leverkusen, 19 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 ng\u00e0y ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1992 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u00c1o s\u1ed1 19 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 Santi Cazorla, song c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chia tay \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Emirates.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBernd Leno v\u1eabn c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111eo \u00e1o s\u1ed1 1 \u1edf Arsenal, nh\u01b0ng anh ph\u1ea3i ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ebfn khi Petr Cech r\u1eddi s\u00e2n Emirates. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi S\u00e9c c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 1 n\u0103m v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Leno \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1eadt Petr Cech</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-arsenal-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-tan-binh-thu-3-172-190220.html\" target=\"_blank\">Arsenal mua Leno</span> v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 h\u01a1n 20 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0a th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh n\u00e0y v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. Petr Cech m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed, song nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng anh s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb cho c\u1ef1u sao Bayer Leverkusen \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bernd Leno\" title=\"Bernd Leno\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/arsenal-sap-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-bernd-leno.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Bernd Leno \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u1edbi Petr Cech</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y Leno \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1eadt Petr Cech qua \u0111\u00f3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed s\u1ed1 1 trong khung g\u1ed7. HLV Unai Emery c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1eafp x\u1ebfp \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 hai c\u00f9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, Leno b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh c\u00f2n Cech b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh \u1edf c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00fap. V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c David Ospina s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u00ecm b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi, b\u1edfi \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i anh ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n s\u1ed1 3 c\u1ee7a Arsenal m\u00e0 th\u00f4i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4100","checkdouble":"190840"},{"date":"07:44 10/07","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 10/7: 48 gi\u1edd n\u1eefa, Ronaldo s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Juve","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/10/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-ngay-107-48-gio-nua-ronaldo-se-la-nguoi-cua-juve.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 10/7.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Chelsea t\u00ednh \"h\u1edbt tay tr\u00ean\" m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau Man City. </strong>Theo t\u1edd Tuttosport, Chelsea \u0111ang t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t Man City trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Jorginho c\u1ee7a Napoli. L\u1ee3i th\u1ebf c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London l\u00e0 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u00f3n Maurizio Sarri, th\u1ea7y c\u0169 c\u1ee7a Jorginho t\u1edbi s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge thay Antonio Conte. Ngo\u00e0i ra, Chelsea tin \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 60 tri\u1ec7u Euro c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd l\u00e0 kh\u00f3 kh\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1eeb.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>48 gi\u1edd n\u1eefa, Ronaldo s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Juve. </strong>Theo Sky Sports, th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Cristiano Ronaldo sang Juventus s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111o\u1ea1t trong v\u00f2ng 48 gi\u1edd n\u1eefa. \u0110\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Ronaldo, Jorge Mendes v\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Real Madrid, Florentino Perez s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p nhau trong ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u00f2n t\u1ed3n \u0111\u1ecdng. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n thi\u1ebfu c\u00e1i g\u1eadt \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u s\u00e2n Bernabeu.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 107 48 gi\u1edd n\u1eefa, Ronaldo s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 107 48 gi\u1edd n\u1eefa, Ronaldo s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/Ronaldo-toi-Juventus.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ronaldo chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Juventus</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Lewandowski \u1edf l\u1ea1i Bayern. </strong>Ban \u0111\u1ea7u, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Pini Zahavi c\u1ee7a Robert Lewandowski tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 anh mu\u1ed1n t\u00ecm m\u1ed9t th\u1eed th\u00e1ch m\u1edbi. Nh\u01b0ng sau m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t v\u1edbi Ba Lan, nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb kh\u1ee7ng d\u00e0nh cho Lewy c\u0169ng v\u01a1i b\u1edbt. Anh nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i Bayern ph\u1ee5ng s\u1ef1 t\u00e2n HLV Niko Kovac.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>T\u00e2n binh Juventus m\u1eddi g\u1ecdi Ronaldo n\u1ed1i g\u00f3t. </strong>Emre Can m\u1edbi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ra m\u1eaft Juventus. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd th\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi n\u1ebfu Cristiano Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin. Juve m\u1edbi g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb 100 tri\u1ec7u Euro t\u1edbi Real \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Ronaldo v\u00e0 \u0111ang ch\u1edd c\u00e1i g\u1eadt \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Florentino Perez.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>\u0110\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 Sterling b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch. </strong>Raheem Sterling \u0111ang nh\u1eadn ph\u1ea3i nhi\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch b\u1edfi phong \u0111\u1ed9 ngh\u00e8o n\u00e0n v\u00e0 b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110T Anh. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i Eric Dier v\u1eabn d\u00e0nh cho ng\u00f4i sao Man City nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi c\u00f3 c\u00e1nh. Anh tin c\u00e1ch \u1ee9ng ph\u00f3 v\u1edbi t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a Sterling l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sterling\" title=\"Sterling\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/bo-doi-huyen-thoai-mu-bao-ve-sao-man-city-o-world-cup.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u0110\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u1ee3i khen c\u00e1ch Sterling \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u00f3 \u00e1p l\u1ef1c</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xavi \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha sa th\u1ea3i Lopetegui. </strong>Vi\u1ec7c sa th\u1ea3i HLV Julen Lopetegui ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m World Cup 2018 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng tr\u00e1i chi\u1ec1u trong d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn T\u00e2y Ban Nha. Ri\u00eang v\u1edbi ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Xavi, anh \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Real Madrid.<br>\r\n\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 <br>\r\n<strong>C\u1ef1u th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f3 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi.</strong> Jack Wilshere \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i l\u1eddi chia tay Arsenal sau m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18. C\u1ef1u th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng x\u1ee9 s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9 m\u1edbi k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 3 n\u0103m v\u1edbi West Ham d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 do.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p (TTVN)<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4099","checkdouble":"190814"},{"date":"06:47 10/07","title":"Hazard: \u201cT\u1edbi Real Madrid l\u00e0 gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 c\u1ee7a m\u1ecdi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7\u201d","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/2/hazard-toi-real-madrid-la-giac-mo-cua-moi-cau-thu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Eden Hazard ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Real Madrid v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ed9. Gi\u1eefa nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh t\u1ea1i Chelsea, ng\u00f4i sao tuy\u1ec3n B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u01a1i cho Real l\u00e0 gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 c\u1ee7a m\u1ecdi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Real \u0111\u01b0a Hazard v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nEden Hazard \u0111ang l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi truy\u1ec1n c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng gi\u00fap B\u1ec9 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018. V\u00e0o \u0111\u00eam nay, anh v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Ph\u00e1p t\u1ea1i St Petersburg. \u0110\u1ec3 t\u1edbi v\u00f2ng n\u00e0y, B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n phong \u0111\u1ed9 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi v\u1edbi 5 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1 th\u00eam gi\u1edd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch s\u1ed1 1 l\u00e0 Brazil trong s\u1ef1 kinh ng\u1ea1c c\u1ee7a d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn. V\u1edbi kh\u00ed th\u1ebf c\u1ef1c cao, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chinh ph\u1ee5c c\u00fap v\u00e0ng World Cup l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed. N\u1ebfu \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 x\u1ea3y ra, \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u00ean Hazard l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u cho danh hi\u1ec7u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t gi\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Eden Hazard ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Real Madrid v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ed9 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Eden Hazard ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Real Madrid v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ed9 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/Eden-Hazard-phat-bieu-ve-Real-Madrid-voi-su-nguong-mo-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Hazard t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i World Cup trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o B\u1ec9</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNgay t\u1eeb th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, uy t\u00edn c\u1ee7a Hazard \u0111\u00e3 gia t\u0103ng \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3. Anh l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a Real Madrid, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb n\u00f3i l\u1eddi chia tay Cristiano Ronaldo (chuy\u1ec3n sang Juventus).<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Hazard l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 Real</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e2y gi\u1edd, nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Hazard c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 sang Real m\u1edbi xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n. D\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Zinedine Zidane, m\u1ed9t th\u1ea7n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Hazard, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ed9 l\u00ean kh\u00f4ng \u00edt l\u1ea7n. V\u00e0 gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p Zidane \u0111\u00e3 chia tay Los Blancos sau chung k\u1ebft Champions League m\u00f9a 2017/18, anh v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u1ecf c\u00e1nh c\u1eeda t\u1edbi Santiago Bernabeu.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Hazard\" title=\"Hazard\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/eden-hazard-tu-tin-se-lam-tot-hon-messi-ronaldo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Hazard ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Real Madrid v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ed9</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Real c\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i gi\u1ea3m \u0111i m\u01a1 \u01b0\u1edbc n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 Zidane?&rdquo;, Hazard ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Real Madrid tr\u00ean beIN SPORTS. &ldquo;Zidane l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 Real l\u00e0 gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 c\u1ee7a m\u1ecdi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. Zidane hay kh\u00f4ng Zidane, chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o tr\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Real v\u1eabn l\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Nh\u01b0ng chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o m\u00e0u xanh c\u1ee7a Chelsea c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi t\u00f4i. T\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y phi\u1ec1n n\u1ebfu \u1edf l\u1ea1i. B\u00e2y gi\u1edd, \u0111ang l\u00e0 World Cup. Nh\u01b0 t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i kh\u00f4ng d\u01b0\u1edbi 100 l\u1ea7n, t\u00f4i \u0111ang \u1edf Chelsea v\u00e0 cho \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o \u0111\u01b0a ra \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-tuyen-bo-khong-mua-mbappe-180-190795.html\">Th\u1ef1c h\u01b0 chuy\u1ec7n Real chi 230 tri\u1ec7u euro mua Mbappe?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/diem-qua-5-ngoi-sao-tan-cong-co-the-the-cho-ronaldo-tai-real-madrid-180-190789.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m qua 5 ng\u00f4i sao c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ebf ch\u1ed7 Ronaldo t\u1ea1i Real Madrid</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/real-madrid-tranh-gianh-milinkovicsavic-voi-mu-172-190704.html\">Real Madrid tranh gi\u00e0nh Milinkovic-Savic v\u1edbi M.U</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/modric-khong-tin-ronaldo-se-roi-real-180-190697.html\">Modric kh\u00f4ng tin Ronaldo s\u1ebd r\u1eddi Real</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sadio-mane-noi-gi-khi-duoc-real-madrid-quan-tam-172-190673.html\">Sadio Mane n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Real Madrid quan t\u00e2m</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4098","checkdouble":"190811"},{"date":"07:04 10/07","title":"Luis Enrique l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1eafn cho \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/10/luis-enrique-la-lua-chon-dung-dan-cho-dt-tay-ban-nha.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Michel Salgado ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Enrique sau khi l\u00ean ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n chi\u1ebfc gh\u1ebf HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha. C\u1ef1u tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 La Roja kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1eafn c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n. </h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Enrique ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n \u0110T TBN</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1ed1i qua, Luis Enrique \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh HLV \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha. \u00d4ng \u0111\u1eb7t b\u00fat k\u00fd v\u00e0o b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 2 n\u0103m d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f2. Quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a ra b\u1edfi ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Luis Rubiales c\u1ee7a Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 T\u00e2y Ban Nha (RFEF) sau m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c h\u1ecdp c\u1ea5p cao.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nLuis Enrique thay th\u1ebf Fernando Hierro, ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1ea1m ng\u1ed3i gh\u1ebf HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. Ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u, RFEF \u0111\u00e3 sa th\u1ea3i HLV Julen Lopetegui do nh\u1eefng l\u00f9m x\u00f9m li\u00ean quan t\u1edbi \u0111\u01a1n ph\u01b0\u01a1ng gia nh\u1eadp Real Madrid.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Salgado ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Enrique, t\u00e2n HLV T\u00e2y Ban Nha h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Salgado ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Enrique, t\u00e2n HLV T\u00e2y Ban Nha h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/Luis-Enrique-len-DT-TBN.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Salgado ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Enrique v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u00e2m l\u00fd b\u1ecb x\u00e1o tr\u1ed9n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do ch\u00ednh d\u1eabn t\u1edbi T\u00e2y Ban Nha ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. H\u1ecd ch\u1eadt v\u1eadt v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0 sau \u0111\u00f3 l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c d\u1eebng ch\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Salgado \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 Enrique</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3, c\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 Michel Salgado c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y Luis Enrique c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi Hierro, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng T\u00e2y Ban Nha trong ho\u00e0n c\u1ea3nh kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. \u201c\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng, \u00f4ng \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng HLV c\u00f3 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha\u201d, Salgado ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Enrique trong m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a FIFA.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cEnrique \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ea1i Barcelona v\u1edbi c\u00fa \u0103n 3, l\u00e0 HLV t\u1ef1 do v\u00e0 trong th\u1eddi kh\u1eafc r\u1ea5t thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i. B\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n ai \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn, b\u00ecnh t\u0129nh b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u m\u1ed9t d\u1ef1 \u00e1n m\u1edbi. Nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u l\u1ea1i, b\u1edfi th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m l\u1ea1i t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u. Kh\u00f4ng gi\u1ed1ng Hierro trong 2 ng\u00e0y, Enrique c\u00f3 c\u1ea3 m\u1ed9t n\u0103m chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb v\u00e0 t\u00f4i mong \u0111\u1ee3i r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u t\u1eeb T\u00e2y Ban Nha.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/xavi-phat-bieu-ve-ghe-hlv-tay-ban-nha-180-190785.html\">Xavi ch\u01b0a s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho chi\u1ebfc gh\u1ebf HLV T\u00e2y Ban Nha</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/chinh-thuc-fernando-hierro-roi-ghe-hlv-truong-cua-tbn-421-190705.html\">CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: Fernando Hierro r\u1eddi gh\u1ebf HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a TBN</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/rakitic-phat-bieu-ve-iniesta-421-190625.html\">\u0110\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169 cho\u00e1ng v\u00e1ng khi Iniesta b\u1ecb TBN h\u1eaft h\u1ee7i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/goc-nhin-world-cup-2018/world-cup-2018-3-cau-thu-gay-that-vong-nhat-cua-dt-tay-ban-nha-466-190435.html\">World Cup 2018: 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/dt-anh-giong-voi-tay-ban-nha-nam-2010-421-190424.html\">\u0110T Anh gi\u1ed1ng v\u1edbi T\u00e2y Ban Nha n\u0103m 2010</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4097","checkdouble":"190812"},{"date":"07:25 10/07","title":"Sao tr\u1ebb Real Madrid b\u00e1o tin bu\u1ed3n cho M.U v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea1i gia","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/10/sao-tre-real-madrid-bao-tin-buon-cho-mu-va-cac-dai-gia.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Marco Asensio s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i Real Madrid thay v\u00ec chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Man United hay m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ea1i gia n\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. Ch\u00ednh \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 v\u1edbi b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Asensio \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i ch\u01a1i cho Espanyol d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n (2015/16) v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Marco Asensio \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Real Madrid. Anh t\u1ea1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi HLV Zinedine Zidane v\u00e0 ng\u00e0y m\u1ed9t c\u00f3 vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n. Nh\u01b0 m\u00f9a 2017/18 v\u1eeba qua, Asensio xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u1edf 53 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cho Real tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nAsensio ng\u00e0y m\u1ed9t ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 h\u01a1n t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Santiago Bernabeu. M\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, anh \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p 11 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cho Real ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3 7 pha ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o. Qua \u0111\u00f3, ch\u00e0ng trai 22 tu\u1ed5i l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Marco Asensio s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i Real Madrid thay v\u00ec t\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea1i gia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Marco Asensio s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i Real Madrid thay v\u00ec t\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea1i gia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/26/Marco-Asensio-se-o-lai-Real-Madrid-thay-vi-toi-cac-dai-gia-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Asensio \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i gia \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00cdt nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 4 \u0111\u1ea1i gia bao g\u1ed3m Man United, Liverpool, Chelsea v\u00e0 PSG \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Asensio. \u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 l\u00fac Real t\u1eebng t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n sao tr\u1ebb n\u00e0y b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb l\u00ean t\u1edbi 150 tri\u1ec7u Euro.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Nh\u01b0ng s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i Real</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1ea5u ch\u1ed1t v\u1eabn n\u1eb1m \u1edf c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n Marco Asensio. Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i m\u1ecdi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng n\u00e0y mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i, s\u1ebd thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng theo \u0111u\u1ed5i. Tuy nhi\u00ean, quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a Asensio th\u00f4ng qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Horacio Gaggioli l\u00e0 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Real.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tien ve Asensio\" title=\"tien ve Asensio\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/tien-ve-Asensio.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u0110\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o Asensio s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i Real Madrid</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cMarco Asensio s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i Real Madrid, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111i \u0111\u00e2u\u201d, Gaggioli n\u00f3i v\u1edbi Calciomercato. \u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111ang ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n theo th\u1eddi gian. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng \u1edf Madrid.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Cristiano Ronaldo chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb r\u1eddi Real xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n ng\u00e0y m\u1ed9t nhi\u1ec1u. Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh hi\u1ec7n th\u1ef1c, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn Los Blancos s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ea3 Asensio. V\u1ec1 ph\u1ea7n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y, \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 anh v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean t\u1ea7m tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t Real. H\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Asensio v\u1edbi B\u1ea7y k\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n t\u1edbi t\u1eadn n\u0103m 2023 sau l\u1ea7n gia h\u1ea1n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t n\u0103m 2017.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hazard-toi-real-madrid-la-giac-mo-cua-moi-cau-thu-421-190811.html\">Hazard: \u201cT\u1edbi Real Madrid l\u00e0 gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 c\u1ee7a m\u1ecdi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7\u201d</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-tuyen-bo-khong-mua-mbappe-180-190795.html\">Th\u1ef1c h\u01b0 chuy\u1ec7n Real chi 230 tri\u1ec7u euro mua Mbappe?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/diem-qua-5-ngoi-sao-tan-cong-co-the-the-cho-ronaldo-tai-real-madrid-180-190789.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m qua 5 ng\u00f4i sao c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ebf ch\u1ed7 Ronaldo t\u1ea1i Real Madrid</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/real-madrid-tranh-gianh-milinkovicsavic-voi-mu-172-190704.html\">Real Madrid tranh gi\u00e0nh Milinkovic-Savic v\u1edbi M.U</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/modric-khong-tin-ronaldo-se-roi-real-180-190697.html\">Modric kh\u00f4ng tin Ronaldo s\u1ebd r\u1eddi Real</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4096","checkdouble":"190813"}]}